    <p>The 35-year-old hu­man rights lawyer rep­re­sents po­lit­i­cal ac­tivists and lese ma­jeste de­fen­dants in court.</p>
    <p>Dur­ing an Aug 3 rally, he shook Thai­land by openly call­ing for the monarch’s pow­ers to be trimmed.</p>
    <p>Since then, he has fre­quently re­peated his mes­sage, open­ing the way for pub­lic dis­cus­sion on the role of Thai­land’s monar­chy.</p>

